item.description: We will be relaxing and enjoying drinks/dinner and fun times! Each person pays for their own food/drink. Join us for a great time with friendly people!
item.how_to_find_us: Look for Catherine (see photo). We will be in the bar area for drinks, then move to the dining room. If you have trouble finding us, please call cell 774 232 0000.
item.why: Come join us for a fun and relaxing time- meeting new people, catching up with friends and enjoying good food and drinks. Joint event with the 25+ Social Fun Group.
item.name: Drinks, Dinner and Good Times at Legal Seafood
